Mike Kleinhenz https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mike_Kleinhenz 0 Michael Anthony Kleinhenz (November 14, 1951 – July 11, 2008) was an American voice actor who frequently participated in translation and dubbing of Japanese anime. His voice also appeared in national TV and radio advertisements and local advertisements in the Houston area.
